1
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:24,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dang, that thing's the real deal.</font>

2
00:00:24,340 --> 00:00:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is such a messed up job. Seriously.</font>

3
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:30,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I bet I'll breeze through it.</font>

4
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 10: REUNION</font>

5
00:02:03,860 --> 00:02:05,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"To Miss Witch,</i></font>

6
00:02:05,630 --> 00:02:07,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Have you been well?</i></font>

7
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:09,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In the time that you've been away,</i></font>

8
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the air and water in 
the town have turned filthy.</i></font>

9
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My body is in such pain that I can't 
go outside, so every day is depressing."</i></font>

10
00:02:31,490 --> 00:02:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I dearly wish that you 
would visit again soon."</i></font>

11
00:02:36,210 --> 00:02:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The owner of the bookstore 
sent a kind of SOS letter,</i></font>

12
00:02:40,570 --> 00:02:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so Miss Witch decided to visit the city
 for the first time in a while.</i></font>

13
00:02:51,420 --> 00:02:54,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You oughta give up on going to town.</font>

14
00:02:54,530 --> 00:02:58,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The End of All Things showed up near 
the border recently and thanks to that,</font>

15
00:02:58,060 --> 00:03:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">refugees have been pouring into 
the city, so things aren't looking good.</font>

16
00:03:02,740 --> 00:03:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The crow tried to stop her.</i></font>

17
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there some reason why 
you still want to go</font>

18
00:03:09,090 --> 00:03:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even if it might mean 
facing danger, Miss Witch?</font>

19
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:17,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he sent a letter, it must be serious.</font>

20
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, he said he was in pain, so 
I want to bring him some medicine.</font>

21
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:25,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Miss Witch...</i></font>

22
00:03:26,070 --> 00:03:27,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to go.</font>

23
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, there's more to it than that, right?</font>

24
00:03:31,790 --> 00:03:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've never gotten a letter 
from a human before now.</font>

25
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:39,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You let it go to your head and 
now you can't stop yourself.</font>

26
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse.</i></font>

27
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What? Is that why?!</i></font>

28
00:03:44,540 --> 00:03:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse.</i></font>

29
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No. Absolutely wrong.</font>

30
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse.</i></font>

31
00:03:49,610 --> 00:03:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chomping at the bit after 
one pathetic little letter.</font>

32
00:03:53,100 --> 00:03:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What an easy woman!</font>

33
00:03:55,060 --> 00:03:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, all you are to that 
book guy is a cleaning lady.</font>

34
00:03:59,050 --> 00:04:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse.</i></font>

35
00:04:00,850 --> 00:04:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. You must have always 
wanted a pen pal, Miss Witch.</font>

36
00:04:02,550 --> 00:04:08,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse.</i></font>

37
00:04:06,890 --> 00:04:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No kidding. That's adorbs! How precious!</font>

38
00:04:12,530 --> 00:04:19,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But to be honest, I don't want 
Miss Witch to go to town, either.</i></font>

39
00:04:19,090 --> 00:04:22,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What're all these nasty 
mushrooms poppin' up fer?</font>

40
00:04:22,330 --> 00:04:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ain't that the Champignon Witch there?</font>

41
00:04:25,010 --> 00:04:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The mushrooms she's sprouting are 
a lot bigger than normal. I wonder why.</i></font>

42
00:04:30,570 --> 00:04:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

43
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ahh!</font>

44
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's talkin'!</font>

45
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run like heck!</font>

46
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her breath's s'posed to be poison!</font>

47
00:04:38,650 --> 00:04:40,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Terrifyin'!</font>

48
00:04:40,590 --> 00:04:43,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's probably no 
point trying to explain.</font>

49
00:04:43,530 --> 00:04:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if the villagers are acting like this,
 I have a bad feeling about the city.</font>

50
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:01,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Careful, Sonny.</font>

51
00:05:01,050 --> 00:05:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you hold onto the witch like that, 
you're gonna get poisoned and die!</font>

52
00:05:04,970 --> 00:05:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon over here.</font>

53
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:11,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be fine.</font>

54
00:05:13,730 --> 00:05:18,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Witch isn't at all dangerous 
like the rumors say.</font>

55
00:05:18,090 --> 00:05:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? I'm the proof of that.</font>

56
00:05:20,770 --> 00:05:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if you leave the mushrooms be, 
they'll wither up on their own.</font>

57
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This should explain everything.</font>

58
00:05:27,170 --> 00:05:29,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh.</font>

59
00:05:33,210 --> 00:05:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did my power help Miss Witch?</i></font>

60
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:43,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was able to protect her, 
even though I'm so small!</i></font>

61
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so glad!</i></font>

62
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna, your right hand and right 
foot are moving together.</font>

63
00:05:58,670 --> 00:06:01,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what were those 
rumors in town all about,</font>

64
00:06:01,510 --> 00:06:05,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">sayin' that black witches summon 
a monster called The End of All Things?</font>

65
00:06:08,450 --> 00:06:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could be a load of bunk, y'know.</font>

66
00:06:09,870 --> 00:06:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You might be right, y'know.</font>

67
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How would we know, y'know?</font>

68
00:06:12,940 --> 00:06:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?</i></font>

69
00:06:14,030 --> 00:06:18,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why do I have this strange feeling again?</i></font>

70
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The End of All Things.</i></font>

71
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Every time I hear that name, 
it wears away my happy feelings</i></font>

72
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and fills my heart with dread.</i></font>

73
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I'm okay.</font>

74
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:44,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I gotta keep it together. 
I have to protect Miss Witch!</i></font>

75
00:07:05,850 --> 00:07:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is... the city?</i></font>

76
00:07:09,780 --> 00:07:14,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}If you touch The End of All Things, 
your skin turns black and rots off</font>

77
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}and the air fills with this stench that,</font>

78
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that man speaking one of 
the refugees from the border</font>

79
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:18,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}if you breathe it, eats away 
at you from the inside.</font>

80
00:07:19,010 --> 00:07:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The land that it poisons 
can't be used for a decade.</font>

81
00:07:20,340 --> 00:07:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who escaped The End of All Things?</font>

82
00:07:23,490 --> 00:07:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heresy and faithlessness 
in your heart</font>

83
00:07:26,010 --> 00:07:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is what attracts The End of All Things.</font>

84
00:07:28,670 --> 00:07:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The End of All Things.</i></font>

85
00:07:30,790 --> 00:07:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The pollution in town is 
even worse than we thought.</font>

86
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gotta be strong and support Luna.</font>

87
00:07:39,590 --> 00:07:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ain't that her? The witch who grows 
all them bad poison mushrooms?</font>

88
00:07:43,620 --> 00:07:45,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna slay her myself!</font>

89
00:07:45,650 --> 00:07:46,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

90
00:07:46,820 --> 00:07:49,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing? 
What if she curses you?!</font>

91
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's what the man at 
the fountain was saying!</font>

92
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She summons The End of All Things 
'cause she's mad about being an outcast.</font>

93
00:07:56,230 --> 00:07:58,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The black witch is an evil heretic!</font>

94
00:07:58,770 --> 00:08:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that true?</font>

95
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My girl ate one of the witch's mushrooms 
and suffered for a whole month!</font>

96
00:08:10,290 --> 00:08:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's wrong!</font>

97
00:08:12,210 --> 00:08:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begone, you cursed demon!</font>

98
00:08:15,670 --> 00:08:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't!</font>

99
00:08:30,690 --> 00:08:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A hand grew out of the ground!</font>

100
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A dead man's hand!</font>

101
00:08:35,260 --> 00:08:38,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy oh boy, oh boy.</font>

102
00:08:38,420 --> 00:08:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You evil necromancer!</font>

103
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Witch!</font>

104
00:08:46,450 --> 00:08:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it! You don't understand! 
Please listen to me!</font>

105
00:08:51,850 --> 00:08:57,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What now? My charm power 
isn't working on them at all.</i></font>

106
00:08:59,150 --> 00:09:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not at all!</i></font>

107
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:14,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna, let's escape.</font>

108
00:09:15,130 --> 00:09:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no point in growing mushrooms 
here and Lize is acting kind of strange.</font>

109
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't.</font>

110
00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not when the situation is this bad. 
If I don't do what I can now...</font>

111
00:09:28,570 --> 00:09:33,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, moo. You shouldn't be wasting 
any of your time on these meanies.</font>

112
00:09:33,590 --> 00:09:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just leave them be.</font>

113
00:09:37,330 --> 00:09:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lu—</font>

114
00:09:41,530 --> 00:09:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

115
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

116
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Moo?</font>

117
00:09:46,510 --> 00:09:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, Miss Witch?</font>

118
00:09:49,570 --> 00:09:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's too dangerous! Please don't go!</font>

119
00:09:54,750 --> 00:09:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No! I don't like this.</i></font>

120
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I really don't!</i></font>

121
00:10:00,790 --> 00:10:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're gonna grow more? Damn you!</font>

122
00:10:04,350 --> 00:10:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right in front of me,</i></font>

123
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:07,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Nice shot! Got her!</font>

124
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:10,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>something terrible is happening 
to the person I adore!</i></font>

125
00:10:11,340 --> 00:10:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I can't protect her. She protected 
me instead. I couldn't even shield her!</i></font>

126
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why am I so weak?</i></font>

127
00:10:49,220 --> 00:10:51,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think that's going too far?</font>

128
00:10:51,860 --> 00:10:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mushrooms are one thing,</font>

129
00:10:54,170 --> 00:10:57,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the End of All Things stuff 
seems a little far-fetched.</font>

130
00:10:57,900 --> 00:11:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the air around the mushrooms 
always seems like it's clearer.</font>

131
00:11:02,310 --> 00:11:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sure is refreshing.</font>

132
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Stop!</font>

133
00:11:10,370 --> 00:11:11,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's so far away.</font>

134
00:11:12,940 --> 00:11:17,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just remembered something 
Luna told me a long time ago.</font>

135
00:11:17,570 --> 00:11:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was always alone before I came 
to live with her, so I asked her,</font>

136
00:11:21,810 --> 00:11:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Weren't you lonely all the time, Luna?"</font>

137
00:11:24,780 --> 00:11:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And everyone else avoided her.</font>

138
00:11:27,710 --> 00:11:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said, "Why do you try to purify 
the world for people like that?"</font>

139
00:11:32,010 --> 00:11:35,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"If it was me, I'd hate it so much, 
I'd probably curl up and die," I said.</font>

140
00:11:37,420 --> 00:11:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then Luna said...</font>

141
00:11:39,810 --> 00:11:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't alone. The forest was 
always right there with me.</font>

142
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The forest changes with the seasons, 
which is always exciting to see,</font>

143
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the clouds come to greet 
me each and every day.</font>

144
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes rain and snow do, too.</font>

145
00:11:55,640 --> 00:12:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even the moon changes shape every day
 and follows me wherever I go.</font>

146
00:12:01,990 --> 00:12:06,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sun also watches over me 
and gives me its blessing.</font>

147
00:12:07,170 --> 00:12:10,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit trying to act so brave, Luna.</font>

148
00:12:10,740 --> 00:12:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None of those are people. 
They aren't even animals.</font>

149
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just makes me feel sad for you.</font>

150
00:12:16,030 --> 00:12:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm not acting brave though.</font>

151
00:12:19,970 --> 00:12:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes I almost forget it, 
but the truth is I'm not alone,</font>

152
00:12:26,130 --> 00:12:30,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even if my heart has trouble 
recognizing that some days.</font>

153
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:31,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

154
00:12:31,410 --> 00:12:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My body is poisoned and 
I am a black witch,</font>

155
00:12:34,830 --> 00:12:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I will never be able to share 
my life with someone else.</font>

156
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I decided to live for myself alone,</font>

157
00:12:43,470 --> 00:12:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it would start to 
make my heart grow numb,</font>

158
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I would eventually be 
swallowed up by loneliness.</font>

159
00:12:50,230 --> 00:12:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I want to feel connected 
and wanted, even if just a little.</i></font>

160
00:12:54,890 --> 00:12:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However faint it may be, the feeling
 that I'm living to help others</i></font>

161
00:12:59,730 --> 00:13:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is what keeps me alive.</i></font>

162
00:13:02,190 --> 00:13:05,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't simply abandon someone like this.</i></font>

163
00:13:05,450 --> 00:13:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I'm so weak, I'm forcing her
 to walk on alone right now.</i></font>

164
00:13:13,370 --> 00:13:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to become stronger!</i></font>

165
00:13:15,940 --> 00:13:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Strong enough that she never 
has to walk alone again.</i></font>

166
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lize, settle down. You're gonna 
give Hatter an upset tummy.</font>

167
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Strong enough that she doesn't feel she 
has to sacrifice herself for others.</i></font>

168
00:13:22,420 --> 00:13:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That isn't very nice. We can't leave 
here until Luna says so, anyway.</font>

169
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to protect her.</i></font>

170
00:13:28,730 --> 00:13:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But crying here now, unable to move,
 I feel completely inadequate.</i></font>

171
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to be her shield, strong enough 
that she'll keep me by her side always.</i></font>

172
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:44,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if it means I lose everything else,</i></font>

173
00:13:44,990 --> 00:13:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to become a magician strong 
enough to do that for her.</i></font>

174
00:13:51,290 --> 00:13:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, black witch there.</font>

175
00:13:55,090 --> 00:14:00,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you the poison witch growing mushrooms
 that are disturbing the peace here?</font>

176
00:14:00,810 --> 00:14:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh. It's interesting that such a toxic 
witch has slipped through the net</font>

177
00:14:04,460 --> 00:14:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of the black witch hunts that we 
white witches have been carrying out.</font>

178
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:13,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A white magician?</i></font>

179
00:14:23,620 --> 00:14:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A vine?</font>

180
00:14:25,650 --> 00:14:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so strong!</font>

181
00:14:28,580 --> 00:14:31,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have an urgent appointment coming up.</font>

182
00:14:31,260 --> 00:14:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you take over for me 
and toss her into cell block number six?</font>

183
00:14:36,060 --> 00:14:37,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Excellency.</font>

184
00:14:37,870 --> 00:14:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just be sure not to touch her, Henri.</font>

185
00:14:41,040 --> 00:14:43,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sounds like she's got enough 
poison to rot your skin right off.</font>

186
00:14:44,470 --> 00:14:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

187
00:15:02,620 --> 00:15:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Henri?</font>

188
00:15:06,470 --> 00:15:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna.</font>

189
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:23,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, you're coming with me.</font>

190
00:15:24,270 --> 00:15:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do not try to struggle.</font>

191
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you try to run now, it will 
only incite the crowd further</font>

192
00:15:31,420 --> 00:15:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and fuel their suspicions about you.</font>

193
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:35,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Henri...</i></font>

194
00:15:36,110 --> 00:15:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Throw no more stones.</font>

195
00:15:45,160 --> 00:15:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Henri.</i></font>

196
00:15:55,090 --> 00:15:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are the Champignon Witch, aren't you?</font>

197
00:15:59,350 --> 00:16:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should be safe from them now.</font>

198
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

199
00:16:02,610 --> 00:16:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am an officer of the crown and 
a descendant of the white witches,</font>

200
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I unfortunately cannot use magic,</font>

201
00:16:10,860 --> 00:16:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so the only one with the magic to untie 
that vine is the person who cast it.</font>

202
00:16:15,900 --> 00:16:19,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I wonder if your powers as
 a black witch are also enough to do so.</font>

203
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... You must be confused. 
Of course you are. Sorry.</font>

204
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:32,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be all right. The people who are
 after you won't come out this far.</font>

205
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:37,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're injured. That must have hurt.</font>

206
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh! What?!</font>

207
00:16:44,850 --> 00:16:50,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amazing! The wizard who conjured 
that vine is actually very powerful.</font>

208
00:16:51,430 --> 00:16:53,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh. My handkerchief is fine.</font>

209
00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:56,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So much for the terrible poison witch.</font>

210
00:16:57,320 --> 00:17:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't know, this 
is kind of a surprise.</font>

211
00:17:00,790 --> 00:17:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rumors do mention mysterious powers, 
but you're not at all what I imagined.</font>

212
00:17:06,250 --> 00:17:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The instant I laid eyes on you, all I 
could think about was protecting you.</font>

213
00:17:11,540 --> 00:17:17,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I can still tell you're just a normal,
 pretty girl who cries easily.</font>

214
00:17:18,210 --> 00:17:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess you can't believe the rumors.</font>

215
00:17:22,140 --> 00:17:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Henri...</i></font>

216
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-oh. Never mind. We've got to hurry.</font>

217
00:17:27,250 --> 00:17:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can escape from that exit. 
You should be able to get away.</font>

218
00:17:30,890 --> 00:17:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would you do this for me?</font>

219
00:17:34,040 --> 00:17:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not supposed to 
remember me at all.</font>

220
00:17:37,560 --> 00:17:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if they catch you?</font>

221
00:17:40,250 --> 00:17:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be fine. That supervisor from 
before has a terrible memory.</font>

222
00:17:44,990 --> 00:17:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's already forgotten about 
plenty of his prisoners</font>

223
00:17:48,370 --> 00:17:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I pull this off from time to time.</font>

224
00:17:50,820 --> 00:17:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't use magic, but if I play 
my inability and connections right,</font>

225
00:17:54,830 --> 00:18:00,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can come up with plenty of excuses. 
So no need to worry. Just get go—</font>

226
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is going to sound strange,</font>

227
00:18:13,210 --> 00:18:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I feel this isn't 
the first time we've met.</font>

228
00:18:17,320 --> 00:18:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe we met in a dream or a former life.</font>

229
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or maybe I'm only being bewitched 
by your powerful magic.</font>

230
00:18:25,170 --> 00:18:30,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna, I want you to come with me, to 
find what awaits beyond ultimate joy.</font>

231
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:33,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only thing that scares me
 is the thought of losing you.</font>

232
00:18:34,860 --> 00:18:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a wife and a child.</font>

233
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know why I would even 
say that to a girl like you.</font>

234
00:18:40,970 --> 00:18:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... wait. Right.</font>

235
00:18:43,820 --> 00:18:46,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Black witches don't grow old, do they?</font>

236
00:18:46,380 --> 00:18:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. No, that's beside the point.</font>

237
00:18:54,150 --> 00:18:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please be do careful,</font>

238
00:18:56,150 --> 00:18:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cha... um...</font>

239
00:18:58,150 --> 00:19:00,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me your name. Your name!</font>

240
00:19:08,290 --> 00:19:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? The heck is that? Holy moly!</font>

241
00:19:13,560 --> 00:19:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait... something don't feel right.</font>

242
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:19,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess I gotta deal with that first.</font>

243
00:19:21,670 --> 00:19:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? We're out of the hat.</font>

244
00:19:24,320 --> 00:19:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like there's still 
trouble here, though.</font>

245
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if that means 
Luna's magic wore off.</font>

246
00:19:29,780 --> 00:19:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't look like she's back 
yet. I wonder where she is.</font>

247
00:19:33,810 --> 00:19:36,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if something happened.</font>

248
00:19:36,020 --> 00:19:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Witch?</font>

249
00:19:39,900 --> 00:19:41,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Lize!</font>

250
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's dangerous!</font>

251
00:19:43,410 --> 00:19:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Witch! Miss Witch, where are you?</font>

252
00:19:49,460 --> 00:19:50,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

253
00:20:02,410 --> 00:20:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize!</font>

254
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is... that?</font>

255
00:20:15,790 --> 00:20:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What just happened?</font>

256
00:20:17,790 --> 00:20:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay, Lize? 
Did any poison get on you?</font>

257
00:20:21,280 --> 00:20:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, figures.</font>

258
00:20:23,490 --> 00:20:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It already made its way here,</font>

259
00:20:25,910 --> 00:20:29,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a cursed youngling that was 
infected by The End of All Things.</font>

260
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:31,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, this sucks!</font>

261
00:20:31,590 --> 00:20:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I screwed up wiping out 
The End at the border,</font>

262
00:20:35,130 --> 00:20:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and if Flame hears that I sprayed bits 
of it everywhere with that tornado,</font>

263
00:20:39,270 --> 00:20:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he's gonna flip out! 
And that guy's a nightmare!</font>

264
00:20:45,950 --> 00:20:51,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there any way to keep it from him? 
Man, this sucks. What am I gonna do now?</font>

265
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:56,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm seriously not cut out for 
this black magician stuff.</font>

266
00:20:57,240 --> 00:21:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are they always 
nagging about the method?</font>

267
00:21:00,820 --> 00:21:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as it gets done, who cares how?</font>

268
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, this makes me wanna quit.</font>

269
00:21:07,940 --> 00:21:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this guy's problem? 
He does nothing but complain.</font>

270
00:21:11,550 --> 00:21:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He won't stop talking to himself.</i></font>

271
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But when he showed up, 
a strong wind started blowing</i></font>

272
00:21:14,270 --> 00:21:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Maybe I'll run off. But would I really 
get away or would they catch up to me?</font>

273
00:21:18,320 --> 00:21:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and it blew away all of 
the lingering blight.</i></font>

274
00:21:19,010 --> 00:21:20,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Whatever. Guess I'll see how things go.</font>

275
00:21:22,950 --> 00:21:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now it feels like that suffocating 
feeling inside is being washed away.</i></font>

276
00:21:25,210 --> 00:21:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And I got the report that Luna 
was supposed to be here in town,</font>

277
00:21:28,670 --> 00:21:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}so what the heck's that dork doing?</font>

278
00:21:31,290 --> 00:21:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a friend of Luna's?</font>

279
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What's that? Are you 
guys friends with Luna, too?</font>

280
00:21:36,860 --> 00:21:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh crap! Wow. Don't tell her
 what I just said, 'kay?</font>

281
00:21:40,710 --> 00:21:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. Are you one of the Black Magician 
Council members? The Wind Magician?</font>

282
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Whoa. What the... what?</font>

283
00:21:49,700 --> 00:21:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How you know that? 
Who're you guys, anyway?</font>

284
00:21:52,630 --> 00:21:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. Eww. Barf!</font>

285
00:21:54,050 --> 00:21:54,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

286
00:21:56,150 --> 00:21:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must be the wrong guy. He's way too crude.</font>

287
00:21:59,670 --> 00:22:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got a point there.</font>

288
00:22:00,670 --> 00:22:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A Black Magician... Council?</i></font>

289
00:22:00,670 --> 00:22:03,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Huh? Wanna say that again, cow?!</font>

290
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yikes!</font>

291
00:22:04,250 --> 00:22:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Wind Magician?</i></font>

292
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, you guys aren't any help at all.
 Where is Luna, anyway?</font>

293
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:12,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I already know.</font>

294
00:22:13,810 --> 00:22:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoosh!</font>

295
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

296
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

297
00:22:26,820 --> 00:22:27,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

298
00:22:30,530 --> 00:22:31,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

299
00:22:38,370 --> 00:22:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: MICHAEL ARNOLD</font>

300
00:22:41,790 --> 00:22:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SUBTITLE TIMING: ANDY ELLIS
EDITING: ELISABETH CRIST</font>

301
00:22:47,760 --> 00:22:52,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CHECK: GABRIELLA ALABANZA
TRANSLATION CHECK: MICHELLE TYMON</font>

302
00:24:06,630 --> 00:24:10,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NEXT TIME: THE COUNCILOR</font>

